    "longBusinessSummary": "Sea & Air Freight International provides multimodal transportation, logistics, shipping brokers and shipping agents, moving, and commercial services in Vietnam and internationally. The company offers sea freight agency, air transport agency, sea and air combined service, road and rail transport, and consolidation service. It also provides door-to-door freight service; customs broker; domestic and bonded transportation; warehousing and distribution; customs clearance procedures, delivery, and transportation of construction, in transit, and exhibition goods. In addition, the company offers shipping agent, goods handling agent, ship charter broker, supply of ships, goods counting service, and crew change service; and packing goods and warehousing, as well as domestic and international moving services. Further, it engages in the intermediation and trade promotion; import and export activities; and supply chain management solutions. Sea & Air Freight International was founded in 1992 and is headquartered in Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam.",
